import React from 'react';
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Tab, Tabs, MyList, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon} from '@mui/material/';
import { ShoppingCartOutlinedIcon } from '@mui/material/IconButton'

export const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <AppBar>
                <Toolbar>
                    <Typography>CineNumen</Typography>
                            <Tabs>
                                <Tab label='Cartelera' />
                            </Tabs>
                            <Tabs>
                                <Tab label='Salas' />
                            </Tabs>
                            <Tabs>
                                <Tab label='Sucursales' />
                            </Tabs>
                            <Tabs>
                                <Tab label='Contacto' />
                            </Tabs>
                            <MyList tipe="row">
                                <ListItemButton>
                                    <ListItemIcon>
                                        <ShoppingCartOutlinedIcon />
                                    </ListItemIcon>
                                </ListItemButton>
                            </MyList>
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>
        </>
    )
}
